
THE SOURCE OF THE PL/I VERSION OF ADVENTURE IS IN MEMBER 'PROGRAM'
WHICH CONTAINS THE PL/I MAINLINE AND SUBROUTINES.

SEE MEMBER 'PGMCOMP' FOR THE COMPILATION JOB STREAM.  THE JOB ALSO
REFERENCES THE NECESSARY OBJECT AND SOURCE MEMBERS FOR ASSEMBLER AND
FORTRAN SUBROUTINES.

FOR Y2K THE DATE() CALLS HAVE BEEN REPLACED BY DATETIME().
(ALL EXCEPT ONE OF THE TIME() CALLS HAS ALSO BEEN REMOVED.)

THE Y2K COMPILATION USED PL/I FOR OS/390 AND VM 1.1.1.

